'''L-5''' was the callsign of [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] when he crash-landed in the polar region of [[Ota]]. He used it to contact the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] base on Ota's equator when, in pursuit of a damaged [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighter]], his [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|T-65 X-wing starfighter]] was hit by falling ice chunks and forced to crash.

